des:
Amazon Alexa and the CONALUX WIFI Smart home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.

You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 

After connecting Alexa to your CONALUX WIFI Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " CONALUX WIFI " app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one CONALUX WIFI account in our " CONALUX WIFI " app;
(3). You need to have some CONALUX WIFI Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our CONALUX WIFI app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in CONALUX WIFI skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search " CONALUX WIFI" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of CONALUX WIFI and you'll be navigated to CONALUX WIFI login page;
(9). Input your CONALUX WIFI account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"

Currently this skill supports products:
smart switch,
smart socket, 
smart bulb....
